The paper discusses the incorporation of bibliometric techniques into information retrieval processes in digital libraries, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and digital libraries (cs.DL). The paper also mentions network analysis (cs.SI), which is a common technique used in bibliometrics. Additionally, the paper touches on issues related to scholarly communication (cs.CY) and science modeling (cs.SD), which are also relevant to bibliometrics.
